  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 7th level the bond you share with your drake intensifies, protecting you and stoking the drake’s fury. When you summon your drake, it grows wings on its back and gains a flying speed equal to its walking speed.</p>\n<p>In addition, while your drake is summoned, you and the drake gain the following benefits:</p>\n<p><strong>Drake Mount.</strong> The drake grows to Medium size. Reflecting your special bond, you can use the drake as a mount if your size is Medium or smaller. While you are riding your drake, it can’t use the flying speed of this feature.</p>\n<p><strong>Magic Fang.</strong> The drake’s Bite attack deals an extra 1d6 damage of the type chosen for the drake’s Draconic Essence.</p>\n<p><strong>Resistance.</strong> You gain resistance to the damage type chosen for the drake’s Draconic Essence.</p>\n<section class=\"secret\">\n<p><em>Note: Be sure to make the appropriate changes to your Drake Companion's sheet when reaching this level.</em></p>\n</section>",
